'''Tel Aviv Zen Center''' is a [[Kwan Um School of Zen]] practice center located in [[Israel]], and is one of four centers in Israel affiliated with the school. The center was established in 1999, by Yuval Gill PSN and the guiding teacher is Zen Master Ji Kwang SSN.
The Center is located at 64 Alenby Street, TEL AVIV, 65812 Israel.  The contact person for the center is Yael Gaathon.  The Center is described as:
Denomination: Korean Chogye Order; Lineage: Seung Sahn; and Affilitaed with: Kwan Um School of Zen<ref>http://iriz.hanazono.ac.jp/zen_centers/centers_data/israel.htm</ref>

